item.description:
@ownage_plz wrote:

The error is pretty obvious … I’ll give you a quick lesson on reading a compiler.

client.java:23028: cannot find symbol

Is telling you that the compiler can’t find the symbol being used in client.java on line 23028. The next bit is telling you the symbols name in this case UseBow and the class it’s in. Then showing you the line. To fix this error either delete the symbol or declare it.
